Some administration pages, like /admin/createsupportzip.action, have help next to each field. Other pages, like /admin/viewgeneralconfig.action, force me to wade through a column on the right to figure out what each field does.

This lookup causes confusion and wastes administrator time. Please be consistent and put inline help next to the field it's describing. If there's too much text for an inline help field, then link to it from the inline help.
